Ronald Lee VALLA, Applicant-Appellant,
v.
STATE of Iowa, Respondent-Appellee. No. 17-1969 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed February 6, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Ronald Valla appeals the denial of his application for post conviction relief. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
